description: Reference libraries for Project Arrhythmia modding
releaseNotes:
# 24.8.4 [alpha]
*Smaller bug fix update but expect new local multiplayer UI and improvements to parallax objects to come next update~*

## Improvements
- Fixed numerous issues with errors / warnings in player logs.

## Fixes
- Fix for metadata preview button becoming stuck in some cases.
- Fix for issue with album art becoming white.
- Fix for several unhandled errors in the IO setup for audio files in editor.
- Fix for player hit data not reseting on 1 hit / 1 life.
- Fix for level end screen sticking around (again).
- Remove all dangerous rich text from description in song panel.
- Fix for some situations where the editor would infinitely load while creating a level.
- Minor UI / UX improvements.

# [Alpha] -> [Default]
This build is a release candidate build for default. Assuming no major / game breaking bugs are found within 2 days, this build will be promoted to default.
